review.classdesign.jammy.core.webservice

Class Problem

  • java.lang.Object
    • review.classdesign.jammy.common.NamedObject
      • review.classdesign.jammy.core.webservice.Problem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Problem
extends NamedObject
    POJO that aims to be bind to the /ContestInfo request, using Gson API. Problem instance belong to a ContestInfo object, and consists in the problem metadata such a name, description, and IO details.
